s=screen DL=screen.drawLine SC=screen.setColor DR=screen.drawRect DRF=screen.drawRectF DT=screen.drawTriangle DTF=screen.drawTriangleF DTXT=screen.drawText GN=input.getNumber SN=output.setNumber FMT=string.format SUB=string.sub FLOOR=math.floor
function CLAMP(n,x,y) return math.max(x,math.min(y,n)) end
function onTick() ias=GN(4) alt=GN(5) hdg=GN(6) vs=GN(7) ralt=GN(8) falt=GN(9) vs0=GN(10) vno=GN(11) vne=GN(12)
vne=CLAMP(vne-ias+14,0,29) vno=CLAMP(vno-ias+14,0,29) vs0=CLAMP(vs0-ias+14,0,29)
off=(alt%10)/10*6 alt=FLOOR((alt-5)/10+0.5)*10 end
function zero(x,y) DR(x,y,2,4) end function one(x,y) DL(x+1,y,x+1,y+4) DL(x,y+4,x+3,y+4) DL(x,y+1,x+1,y+1) end function two(x,y) DL(x,y,x+3,y) DL(x,y+2,x+3,y+2) DL(x,y+4,x+3,y+4) DL(x+2,y,x+2,y+2) DL(x,y+2,x,y+4) end function three(x,y) DL(x,y,x+3,y) DL(x,y+2,x+3,y+2) DL(x,y+4,x+3,y+4) DL(x+2,y,x+2,y+4) end function four(x,y) DL(x,y+2,x+3,y+2) DL(x+2,y,x+2,y+5) DL(x,y,x,y+2) end function five(x,y) DL(x,y,x+3,y) DL(x,y+2,x+3,y+2) DL(x,y+4,x+3,y+4) DL(x,y,x,y+2) DL(x+2,y+2,x+2,y+4) end function six(x,y) DR(x,y+2,2,2) DL(x,y,x+3,y) DL(x,y,x,y+2) end function seven(x,y) DL(x,y,x+3,y) DL(x+2,y,x+2,y+5) end function eight(x,y) DR(x,y,2,4) DL(x,y+2,x+3,y+2) end function nine(x,y) DR(x,y,2,2) DL(x+2,y,x+2,y+5) DL(x,y+4,x+3,y+4) end
--convert to small number function CSN(x,y,n) if n=="0" then zero(x,y) elseif n=="1" then one(x,y) elseif n=="2" then two(x,y) elseif n=="3" then three(x,y) elseif n=="4" then four(x,y) elseif n=="5" then five(x,y) elseif n=="6" then six(x,y) elseif n=="7" then seven(x,y) elseif n=="8" then eight(x,y) elseif n=="9" then nine(x,y) end end
--draw small numbers function DSN(x,y,s) s=tostring(s) l=string.len(s) for i=1,l do n=s:sub(i,i) CSN(x,y,n) x=x+4 end end
function onDraw() w=s.getWidth() h=s.getHeight() a=w/2 b=h/2
--IAS SC(20,20,20,170) DRF(0,b-14,14,29) SC(5,5,5) DRF(0,b-3,14,7) SC(220,220,220) DSN(2,b-2, FMT("%03i",ias))--white
SC(70,70,70) DSN(2,b-14,FMT("%03i",ias+2)) DSN(2,b-8, FMT("%03i",ias+1)) --DSN(2,b-2, FMT("%03i",ias)) if ias>0 then DSN(2,b+4, FMT("%03i",ias-1)) end if ias>1 then DSN(2,b+10,FMT("%03i",ias-2)) end --overspeed SC(200,0,0) DL(0,b+14,0,b-15) --V speeds SC(255,130,0) DL(0,b+14,0,b+14-vne) SC(0,200,0) DL(0,b+14,0,b+14-vno) SC(200,0,0) DL(0,b+14,0,b+14-vs0)
--Alt SC(20,20,20,170) DRF(w-17,b-14,17,29) SC(5,5,5) DRF(w-17,b-3,21,7) DRF(w-8,b-14,8,29) SC(220,220,220) --10 ft DSN(w-8,b+off-14,FMT("%02i",SUB(FLOOR(alt+20),-2))) DSN(w-8,b+off-8, FMT("%02i",SUB(FLOOR(alt+10),-2))) DSN(w-8,b+off-2, FMT("%02i",SUB(FLOOR(alt),-2))) if alt>9 then DSN(w-8,b+off+4,FMT("%02i",SUB(FLOOR(alt-10),-2))) end if alt>19 and off<0.5 then DSN(w-8,b+off+10,FMT("%02i",SUB(FLOOR(alt-20),-2))) end --100 ft DSN(w-16,b-2, FMT("%02i",SUB(FLOOR((alt)/100),1,2))) --white SC(70,70,70) DSN(w-16,b-14,FMT("%02i",SUB(FLOOR((alt+200)/100),1,2))) DSN(w-16,b-8, FMT("%02i",SUB(FLOOR((alt+100)/100),1,2))) if alt>99 then DSN(w-16,b+4,FMT("%02i",SUB(FLOOR((alt-100)/100),1,2))) end if alt>199 then DSN(w-16,b+10,FMT("%02i",SUB(FLOOR((alt-200)/100),1,2))) end --extra tape SC(5,5,5) DRF(w-8,b-14,8,4) DRF(w-8,b+11,8,4)
--hdg SC(5,5,5) DRF(a-6,h-7,13,7) SC(220,220,220) DSN(a-5,h-6,FMT("%03i",hdg))
--VS SC(10,10,10) DL(w-1,b,w-1,b+1) SC(250,0,250) if vs>10 then DL(w-1, b-1, w-1, b-vs/200) end if vs<-10 then DL(w-1, b+1, w-1, b-vs/200) end
--rad alt if ralt<1000 then SC(5,5,5,150) DRF(w-17,b+15,17,7) SC(220,220,220) DSN(w-12,b+16,FMT("%03i",math.min(ralt,-falt))) end end

function drawArc(...) --x,y,radius,(angle1,angle2,filled,step) local x,y,r,a1,a2,pie,step = ... a1 = a1 or 0 a2 = a2 or 360 step = step or 11.25--22.5 if a2<a1 then a2,a1=a1,a2 end local a,px,py,ox,oy,ar = false,0,0,0,0,0 repeat a = a and math.min(a+step,a2) or a1 ar = (a-90)*math.pi /180 px,py = x+r*math.cos(ar), y+r*math.sin(ar) if a~=a1 then if pie then DTF(x,y, ox,oy, px,py) else DL(ox,oy,px,py) end end ox,oy = px,py until(a>=a2) end
function onTick() p=GN(1) -- pitch angle ba1=GN(2) -- bank angle inv=GN(3) -- inverted angle hdg=GN(6) hdg=-hdg-90
if inv>0 then -- check if artificial horizon should be upside down ba = ba1 elseif ba1>0 and inv<=0 then ba = 90+(90-ba1) elseif ba1<0 and inv<=0 then ba = -90+(-90-ba1) else ba = ba1 end
ar =(-ba-90)*math.pi/180 arl=(-ba-5-90)*math.pi/180 arr=(-ba+5-90)*math.pi/180
arl4=(-ba-44-90)*math.pi/180 arr4=(-ba+44-90)*math.pi/180
arl3=(-ba-29-90)*math.pi/180 arr3=(-ba+29-90)*math.pi/180 end
function onDraw() w=s.getWidth() h=s.getHeight() a=w/2 b=h/2
--aircraft cues SC(175,175,0) DTF(a,b,a-5,b+6,a+6,b+6) DRF(a-13,b-1,4,2) DRF(a+10,b-1,4,2) --bank reference SC(250,250,250) DTF(a-2,7,a+3,7,a,4) --bank cue SC(250,250,250) DTF(a+32*math.cos(arl),b+32*math.sin(arl), a+32*math.cos(arr),b+32*math.sin(arr), a+28*math.cos(ar),b+28*math.sin(ar)) --bank arc SC(150,150,150) drawArc(a,b,b-3,-ba-45,-ba+46) --45d cues DL(a+32*math.cos(arl4),b+32*math.sin(arl4), a+29*math.cos(arl4),b+29*math.sin(arl4)) DL(a+32*math.cos(arr4),b+32*math.sin(arr4), a+29*math.cos(arr4),b+29*math.sin(arr4)) --30d DL(a+32*math.cos(arl3),b+32*math.sin(arl3), a+29*math.cos(arl3),b+29*math.sin(arl3)) DL(a+32*math.cos(arr3),b+32*math.sin(arr3), a+29*math.cos(arr3),b+29*math.sin(arr3))
--compass rose SC(250,250,250) drawArc(a,97,40,-32,33) --30d ticks for i=30,330,30 do arS=(hdg+i)*math.pi/180 DL(a+42*math.cos(arS),97+42*math.sin(arS), a+40*math.cos(arS),97+40*math.sin(arS)) end for i=0,270,90 do arL=(hdg+i)*math.pi/180 DL(a+43*math.cos(arL),97+43*math.sin(arL), a+40*math.cos(arL),97+40*math.sin(arL)) end
end

s=screen DL=screen.drawLine SC=screen.setColor DR=screen.drawRect DRF=screen.drawRectF DT=screen.drawTriangle DTF=screen.drawTriangleF GN=input.getNumber SN=output.setNumber
function onTick() p = GN(1) -- pitch angle ba1 = GN(2) -- bank angle inv = GN(3) -- inverted angle if inv>0 then -- check if artificial horizon should be upside down ba = ba1 elseif ba1>0 and inv<=0 then ba = 90+(90-ba1) elseif ba1<0 and inv<=0 then ba = -90+(-90-ba1) else ba = ba1 end end
function onDraw() w = s.getWidth() h = s.getHeight() a1 = h/2+1 -- center height b1 = w/2 -- center width
--p1 = p+a r = 1.5*w o = math.rad(ba) -- bank angle radians soh = math.sin(o) cah = math.cos(o) a = a1+(p*cah) -- center of rotation for horizon x value b = b1+(p*soh) -- center of rotation for horizon y value y1 = r*soh x1 = r*cah r2 = 90+(2*w) x2 = r2*soh y2 = r2*cah
SC(5, 20, 60) DTF(-x1+b, y1+a, x1+b, -y1+a, -x2+b, -y2+a) -- sky SC(25, 10, 0) DTF(-x1+b, y1+a, x1+b, -y1+a, x2+b, y2+a) -- ground SC(255, 255, 255) DL(-x1+b, y1+a-cah, x1+b, -y1+a-cah) -- horizon
cx = -10*soh cy = -10*cah DL((-4*cah)+cx+b, (4*soh)+cy+a, (5*cah)+cx+b, (-5*soh)+cy+a) -- 10 u cx = -20*soh cy = -20*cah DL((-4*cah)+cx+b, (4*soh)+cy+a, (5*cah)+cx+b, (-5*soh)+cy+a) -- 20 u cx = -30*soh cy = -30*cah DL((-4*cah)+cx+b, (4*soh)+cy+a, (5*cah)+cx+b, (-5*soh)+cy+a) -- 30 u cx = -40*soh cy = -40*cah DL((-4*cah)+cx+b, (4*soh)+cy+a, (5*cah)+cx+b, (-5*soh)+cy+a) -- 40 u cx = -50*soh cy = -50*cah DL((-4*cah)+cx+b, (4*soh)+cy+a, (5*cah)+cx+b, (-5*soh)+cy+a) -- 50 u cx = -60*soh cy = -60*cah DL((-4*cah)+cx+b, (4*soh)+cy+a, (5*cah)+cx+b, (-5*soh)+cy+a) -- 60 u cx = -70*soh cy = -70*cah DL((-4*cah)+cx+b, (4*soh)+cy+a, (5*cah)+cx+b, (-5*soh)+cy+a) -- 70 u cx = -80*soh cy = -80*cah DL((-4*cah)+cx+b, (4*soh)+cy+a, (5*cah)+cx+b, (-5*soh)+cy+a) -- 80 u
cx = 10*soh cy = 10*cah DL((-4*cah)+cx+b, (4*soh)+cy+a, (5*cah)+cx+b, (-5*soh)+cy+a) -- 10 d cx = 20*soh cy = 20*cah DL((-4*cah)+cx+b, (4*soh)+cy+a, (5*cah)+cx+b, (-5*soh)+cy+a) -- 20 d cx = 30*soh cy = 30*cah DL((-4*cah)+cx+b, (4*soh)+cy+a, (5*cah)+cx+b, (-5*soh)+cy+a) -- 30 d cx = 40*soh cy = 40*cah DL((-4*cah)+cx+b, (4*soh)+cy+a, (5*cah)+cx+b, (-5*soh)+cy+a) -- 40 d cx = 50*soh cy = 50*cah DL((-4*cah)+cx+b, (4*soh)+cy+a, (5*cah)+cx+b, (-5*soh)+cy+a) -- 50 d cx = 60*soh cy = 60*cah DL((-4*cah)+cx+b, (4*soh)+cy+a, (5*cah)+cx+b, (-5*soh)+cy+a) -- 60 d cx = 70*soh cy = 70*cah DL((-4*cah)+cx+b, (4*soh)+cy+a, (5*cah)+cx+b, (-5*soh)+cy+a) -- 70 d cx = 80*soh cy = 80*cah DL((-4*cah)+cx+b, (4*soh)+cy+a, (5*cah)+cx+b, (-5*soh)+cy+a) -- 80 d
SC(255, 0, 0) cxu1 = -86*soh cyu1 = -86*cah cxu2 = -94*soh cyu2 = -94*cah
cxd1 = 86*soh cyd1 = 86*cah cxd2 = 94*soh cyd2 = 94*cah DL((-7*cah)+cxu1+b, (7*soh)+cyu1+a, (7*cah)+cxu2+b, (-7*soh)+cyu2+a) -- 90 degree X DL((-7*cah)+cxu2+b, (7*soh)+cyu2+a, (7*cah)+cxu1+b, (-7*soh)+cyu1+a) DL((-7*cah)+cxd1+b, (7*soh)+cyd1+a, (7*cah)+cxd2+b, (-7*soh)+cyd2+a) -- -90 degree X DL((-7*cah)+cxd2+b, (7*soh)+cyd2+a, (7*cah)+cxd1+b, (-7*soh)+cyd1+a)
end

scr=screen DL=screen.drawLine SC=screen.setColor GN=input.getNumber SN=output.setNumber DC=screen.drawCircle DRF=screen.drawRectF
function onTick() ias=GN(4) alt=GN(5) vs=GN(7) ralt=GN(8) vs0=GN(10) vne=GN(12) end
function AA(x,y) DC(x+1,y+1,1) DL(x,y+1,x,y+5) DL(x+2,y+1,x+2,y+5) end function BB(x,y) DC(x+1,y+1,1) DC(x+1,y+3,1) DL(x,y,x,y+5) end function CC(x,y) DL(x+1,y,x+3,y) DL(x+1,y+4,x+3,y+4) DL(x,y+1,x,y+4) end function DD(x,y) DL(x,y,x+2,y) DL(x,y+4,x+2,y+4) DL(x,y,x,y+5) DL(x+2,y+1,x+2,y+4) end function EE(x,y) DL(x,y,x+3,y) DL(x,y+2,x+2,y+2) DL(x,y+4,x+3,y+4) DL(x,y,x,y+5) end function FF(x,y) DL(x,y,x+3,y) DL(x,y+2,x+2,y+2) DL(x,y,x,y+5) end function GG(x,y) DL(x,y,x+3,y) DL(x,y+4,x+3,y+4) DL(x,y,x,y+4) DL(x+2,y+3,x+2,y+5) end function HH(x,y) DL(x,y+2,x+3,y+2) DL(x,y,x,y+5) DL(x+2,y,x+2,y+5) end function II(x,y) DL(x,y,x+3,y) DL(x,y+4,x+3,y+4) DL(x+1,y,x+1,y+5) end function JJ(x,y) DL(x,y,x+3,y) DL(x,y+4,x+3,y+4) DL(x+2,y,x+2,y+5) DL(x,y+3,x,y+5) end function KK(x,y) DL(x,y+2,x+2,y+2) DL(x,y,x,y+5) DL(x+2,y,x+2,y+2) DL(x+2,y+3,x+2,y+5) end function LL(x,y) DL(x,y+4,x+3,y+4) DL(x,y,x,y+5) end function MM(x,y) DL(x,y+1,x+3,y+1) DL(x,y,x,y+5) DL(x+2,y,x+2,y+5) end function NN(x,y) DL(x,y,x+3,y) DL(x,y,x,y+5) DL(x+2,y,x+2,y+5) end function OO(x,y) DL(x+1,y,x+2,y) DL(x+1,y+4,x+2,y+4) DL(x,y+1,x,y+4) DL(x+2,y+1,x+2,y+4) end function PP(x,y) DC(x+1,y+1,1) DL(x,y,x,y+5) end function QQ(x,y) DL(x+1,y,x+2,y) DL(x+1,y+3,x+3,y+3) DL(x,y+1,x,y+3) DL(x+2,y+1,x+2,y+5) end function RR(x,y) DC(x+1,y+1,1) DL(x,y,x,y+5) DL(x+2,y+3,x+2,y+5) end function SS(x,y) DL(x+1,y,x+3,y) DL(x,y+4,x+2,y+4) DL(x,y+1,x+3,y+4) end function TT(x,y) DL(x,y,x+3,y) DL(x+1,y,x+1,y+5) end function UU(x,y) DL(x,y+4,x+3,y+4) DL(x,y,x,y+5) DL(x+2,y,x+2,y+5) end function VV(x,y) DL(x+1,y+3,x+1,y+5) DL(x,y,x,y+3) DL(x+2,y,x+2,y+3) end function WW(x,y) DL(x,y+3,x+3,y+3) DL(x,y,x,y+5) DL(x+2,y,x+2,y+5) end function XX(x,y) DL(x+1,y+2,x+2,y+2) DL(x,y,x,y+2) DL(x,y+3,x,y+5) DL(x+2,y,x+2,y+2) DL(x+2,y+3,x+2,y+5) end function YY(x,y) DL(x,y,x,y+2) DL(x+2,y,x+2,y+2) DL(x+1,y+2,x+1,y+5) end function ZZ(x,y) DL(x,y,x+3,y) DL(x,y+4,x+3,y+4) DL(x,y+3,x+3,y) end
--convert to small text function CST(x,y,s) if s=="A" then AA(x,y) elseif s=="B" then BB(x,y) elseif s=="C" then CC(x,y) elseif s=="D" then DD(x,y) elseif s=="E" then EE(x,y) elseif s=="F" then FF(x,y) elseif s=="G" then GG(x,y) elseif s=="H" then HH(x,y) elseif s=="I" then II(x,y) elseif s=="J" then JJ(x,y) elseif s=="K" then KK(x,y) elseif s=="L" then LL(x,y) elseif s=="M" then MM(x,y) elseif s=="N" then NN(x,y) elseif s=="O" then OO(x,y) elseif s=="P" then PP(x,y) elseif s=="Q" then QQ(x,y) elseif s=="R" then RR(x,y) elseif s=="S" then SS(x,y) elseif s=="T" then TT(x,y) elseif s=="U" then UU(x,y) elseif s=="V" then VV(x,y) elseif s=="W" then WW(x,y) elseif s=="X" then XX(x,y) elseif s=="Y" then YY(x,y) elseif s=="Z" then ZZ(x,y) end end
--draw small text function DST(x,y,t) l=string.len(t) for i=1,l do s=t:sub(i,i) CST(x,y,s) x=x+4 end end
function onDraw() w=scr.getWidth() h=scr.getHeight() a=w/2 b=h/2
if ias<vs0 or ias>vne then SC(5,5,5,170) DRF(0,b-21,14,7) SC(255,0,0) DST(2,b-20,"SPD") end
if ralt<1000 then SC(0,200,0) DST(w-16,b+16,"R") end end

function drawArc(...) --x,y,radius,(angle1,angle2,filled,step) local x,y,r,a1,a2,pie,step = ... a1 = a1 or 0 a2 = a2 or 360 step = step or 11.25--22.5 if a2<a1 then a2,a1=a1,a2 end local a,px,py,ox,oy,ar = false,0,0,0,0,0 repeat a = a and math.min(a+step,a2) or a1 ar = (a-90)*math.pi /180 px,py = x+r*math.cos(ar), y+r*math.sin(ar) if a~=a1 then if pie then DTF(x,y, ox,oy, px,py) else DL(ox,oy,px,py) end end ox,oy = px,py until(a>=a2) end
function onTick() hspd=GB(1) halt=GB(2) hhdg=GB(3)
tias=GN(1) talt=GN(2) thdg=GN(3) ias=GN(4) alt=GN(5) hdg=GN(6)
tias=CLAMP(tias-ias+14,0,28) talt=CLAMP(FLOOR(talt/10-alt/10)+14,0,28) thdg=thdg-hdg ar =(thdg-90)*math.pi/180 arl=(thdg-4-90)*math.pi/180 arr=(thdg+4-90)*math.pi/180 end
